Answer:
Antipattern Detected: Functional Decomposition: Using the include relationship

   Constructs Involved: Publish Story, Validate Content Format
   Explanation: The use case "Validate Content Format" is an inclusion use case that is included by only one use case ("Publish Story"). It is not associated with any actor directly, does not include or extend any other use case, is not extended by any use case, and is not involved in any generalization. "Validate Content Format" does not represent a complete service observable to a user — it is merely a decomposed sub-step of the publishing process. This is a textbook instance of functional decomposition via the include relationship, where internal processing logic has been incorrectly elevated to a standalone use case.
